productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
This SMS works quite well. It professionally improves my soccer by a lot.
My co-worker Houston has one of these. He says it looks invisible.
